651
00:33:33,579 --> 00:33:35,547
Look, look, look.

652
00:33:35,547 --> 00:33:36,748
20 percent.

653
00:33:36,748 --> 00:33:39,017
I'll do all the work.

654
00:33:41,353 --> 00:33:43,655
I want half
of whatever you get.

655
00:33:43,655 --> 00:33:45,657
