795
00:41:28,820 --> 00:41:31,690
You want to
teach him a lesson?
Break his glasses.

796
00:41:33,024 --> 00:41:34,860
Cut it out!

797
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:36,762
There are rules to life.

798
00:41:36,762 --> 00:41:38,864
One of the most important
you'll find is--

799
00:41:38,864 --> 00:41:42,801
