touch me, O.K.?

1364
01:10:43,807 --> 01:10:45,008
Why not?

1365
01:10:45,008 --> 01:10:47,344
Take another step,
I'll kill you.

1366
01:10:47,344 --> 01:10:49,846
Albert, why not
