a medic?
No.

1533
01:18:44,888 --> 01:18:46,122
Are you sure
you're o.K.?

1534
01:18:46,122 --> 01:18:50,459
Damn it! Let me talk!

1535
01:18:50,459 --> 01:18:52,328
There's a man inside,

1536
01:18:52,328 --> 01:18:54,964
and-- And
he saved my life.

1537
01:18:54,964 --> 01:18:57,366
He-- He--
