1538
01:18:57,366 --> 01:18:59,435
He-- He wants
to go straight.

1539
01:18:59,435 --> 01:19:03,472
He-- He-- He wants a piece
of the American dream.

1540
01:19:03,472 --> 01:19:06,009
He-- He-- He makes
great cappuccino.

1541
01:19:06,009 --> 01:19:07,310
He--

1542
01:19:07,310 --> 01:19:10,346
